text: Heidi Nepf is an American engineer currently the Donald and Martha Harleman Professor at Massachusetts Institute of Technology, publishing research on fluid mechanics with common citations. Her papers have a high of 916, 577 and 414 and was highly cited in 2016. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Massachusetts Institute of Technology faculty Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Bucknell University alumni Category:Stanford University alumni
